each player on that team to sacrifice, then the chosen creatures are sacrificed simultaneously. If you control six or more lands, repeat this process.£6/13/2017: If a creature has an ability that triggers when it or another creature dies, that ability won’t resolve until after the scheme’s triggered ability has completely resolved.£6/13/2017: If a creature has an ability that triggers when another creature dies, it will see other creatures sacrificed at the same time as it. If it’s sacrificed as one of the first creatures, it won’t see the creatures sacrificed the second time.£6/13/2017: In a Supervillain Rumble game, first the next player in turn order chooses a creature, then each other opponent in turn order does the same. Then the chosen creatures are sacrificed simultaneously. Then repeat this process if you control six or more lands.','S',NULL,'N/A','N/A','N/A',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),('430660','Power Without Equal','E01S','Scheme','C',NULL,'0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'When you set this scheme in motion, draw three cards. You have no maximum hand size until your next turn. If you control six or more lands, you may cast up to three nonland cards from your hand without paying their mana costs.',NULL,NULL,'Christine Choi','15','5','£6/13/2017: The number of lands you control is checked as this scheme’s triggered ability resolves. You can’t play a land during your turn before it resolves.£6/13/2017: If you control six or more lands, you’ll draw three cards and get to cast three spells for free. No player may take any actions between the time you draw three cards and the time you finish casting free spells.£6/13/2017: If you cast a card “without paying its mana cost,” you can’t choose to cast it for any alternative costs, such as emerge costs. You can, however, pay additional costs. If the card has any mandatory additional costs, such as that of Tormenting Voice, you must pay those to cast the card.£6/13/2017: If the card has {X} in its mana cost, you must choose 0 as the value of X when casting it without paying its mana cost.£6/13/2017: You must cast any of the three spells you wish to cast for free while this scheme’s ability is resolving. You’ll have to pay the mana cost of any spells cast later in the turn, even if you cast fewer than three as you resolved this ability. The spells will be added to the stack in the order that you cast them.','S',NULL,'N/A','N/A','N/A',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),('430655','The Mighty Will Fall','E01S','Scheme','C',NULL,'0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'When you set this scheme in motion, choose an opponent with the highest life total among your opponents. That player loses 7 life.','#_"Cry out for your comrades so that they£may join you in misery."_#',NULL,'Volkan Baga','10','5',NULL,'S',NULL,'N/A','N/A','N/A',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),('430662','There Is No Refuge','E01S','Scheme','C',NULL,'0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'When you set this scheme in motion, it deals 3 damage to up to one target creature. Create a 3/3 black Horror creature token.','#_"The dunes smell spilled blood."_#',NULL,'Tomasz Jedruszek','17','5','£6/13/2017: If you choose a target creature and it becomes an illegal target by the time this scheme’s triggered ability would resolve, the entire ability doesn’t resolve. You won’t create a Horror token.£6/13/2017: You can choose to target zero creatures. If you do, you’ll still create the Horror token.£6/13/2017: This scheme’s effect allows you to play an additional land during your main phase. Doing so follows the normal timing rules for playing lands.£6/13/2017: The effects of this scheme’s triggered ability in multiples within the same turn are cumulative. It’s also cumulative with other effects that let you play additional lands, such as that of Explore.','S',NULL,'N/A','N/A','N/A',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),('430663','This World Belongs to Me','E01S','Scheme','C',NULL,'0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'When you set this scheme in motion, draw two cards. You may play an additional land this turn.','#_"Little insects, I have created entire worlds and extinguished twice as many."_#',NULL,'Min Yum','18','5',NULL,'S',NULL,'N/A','N/A','N/A',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),('430664','What''s Yours Is Now Mine','E01S','Scheme','C',NULL,'0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'When you set this scheme in motion, gain control of target creature an opponent controls and untap it.','#_"Vow your allegiance to true power."_#',NULL,'Steve Argyle','19','5','£6/13/2017: You control that creature indefinitely. If the owner of the target creature leaves the game, that creature leaves the game as well.£6/13/2017: You can target and gain control of an untapped creature this way.£6/13/2017: This scheme doesn’t grant haste to the target creature. It won’t be able to attack during this turn unless it has haste or somehow gains haste.£6/13/2017: Auras and Equipment attached to that creature remain attached, but you don’t gain control of them.','S',NULL,'N/A','N/A','N/A',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),('430665','When Will You Learn?','E01S','Scheme','C',NULL,'0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'When you set this scheme in motion, each opponent exiles the top card of their library. You may cast any number of nonland cards exiled this way without paying their mana costs.','#_"Don''t fret, infants. It wouldn''t have worked anyway."_#',NULL,'Yohann Schepacz','20','5','£6/13/2017: If you cast a card “without paying its mana cost,” you can’t choose to cast it for any alternative costs, such as emerge costs. You can, however, pay additional costs. If the card has any mandatory additional costs, such as that of Tormenting Voice, you must pay those to cast the card.£6/13/2017: If the card has {X} in its mana cost, you must choose 0 as the value of X when casting it without paying its mana cost.£6/13/2017: You must cast any of the exiled cards you wish to cast for free while this scheme’s ability is resolving. You can’t wait until later in the turn. Any cards not cast this way remain exiled for the rest of the game. The spells will be added to the stack in the order that you cast them.£6/13/2017: If the owner of one of the exiled cards leaves the game, that card leaves the game as well.£6/13/2017: Now you have learned.','S',NULL,'N/A','N/A','N/A',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,